com.authlete.cbor

Class CBORUri

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.authlete.cbor.CBORItem
      • com.authlete.cbor.CBORValue<URI>
        • com.authlete.cbor.CBORUri

  • public class CBORUri
extends CBORValue<URI>
    CBOR data item whose value is a URI.

    This class is used by the CPUri tag processor.

    See Also:
    RFC 8949 Concise Binary Object Representation (CBOR), 3.4.5.3. Encoded Text, CPUri

    • Constructor Summary

      Constructors 
      Constructor and Description
      CBORUri(URI value)
      A constructor with a URI that this CBOR data item represents.
      CBORUri(URI value, boolean tagged)
      A constructor with a URI that this CBOR data item represents and a boolean flag that indicates whether the encode(OutputStream) method of this instance emits a tag or not.
      CBORUri(URI value, boolean tagged, Number tagNumber)
      A constructor with (1) a URI that this CBOR data item represents, (2) a boolean flag that indicates whether the encode(OutputStream) method of this instance emits a tag or not, and (3) a tag number that is used when a tag is emitted.

      • CBORUri

        public CBORUri(URI value,
               boolean tagged)
        A constructor with a URI that this CBOR data item represents and a boolean flag that indicates whether the encode(OutputStream) method of this instance emits a tag or not.

        This constructor is an alias of CBORUri(value, tagged, 32).

        Parameters:
        value - A URI that this CBOR data item represents.
        tagged - true to let the encode(OutputStream} method emit a tag before writing the text string. false to let the encode(OutputStream) method write the text string only.

      • CBORUri

        public CBORUri(URI value,
               boolean tagged,
               Number tagNumber)
        A constructor with (1) a URI that this CBOR data item represents, (2) a boolean flag that indicates whether the encode(OutputStream) method of this instance emits a tag or not, and (3) a tag number that is used when a tag is emitted.
        Parameters:
        value - A URI that this CBOR data item represents.
        tagged - true to let the encode(OutputStream} method emit a tag before writing the text string. false to let the encode(OutputStream) method write the text string only.
        tagNumber - A tag number to be emitted.
